781
00:41:59,959 --> 00:42:01,399
- Iya.
- Sayang sekali.

782
00:42:02,040 --> 00:42:04,199
Bahkan jika kau kembali
memakai pakaian wanita,…

783
00:42:04,520 --> 00:42:05,959
