815
00:44:03,560 --> 00:44:04,560
- Dong Dong.
- Kakak Ipar.

816
00:44:04,840 --> 00:44:05,760
Kenapa begitu basah?

817
00:44:05,840 --> 00:44:07,439
Nona Li jatuh ke air.

818
00:44:07,639 --> 00:44:09,639
Takutnya terbiasa memakai
pakaian pria.

819
00:44:09,760 --> 00:44:12,479
Tiba-tiba memakai pakaian wanita,
